    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311840/extras/c5d0fb0aacb415aa384af9436c14db0f.poster.avif?t=1771859962\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311840/extras/c5d0fb0aacb415aa384af9436c14db0f.webm?t=1771859962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311840/extras/c5d0fb0aacb415aa384af9436c14db0f.mp4?t=1771859962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Karakuri Ninja VR is a ninja action game in which players fight using weapons and ninjutsu in a virtual reality world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game immerses you in exciting battles against ninja robots and golems in stages inspired by Sengoku-era Japan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311840/extras/dd92cbf48a835996e71cb9c7c016ebad.poster.avif?t=1771859962\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311840/extras/dd92cbf48a835996e71cb9c7c016ebad.webm?t=1771859962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311840/extras/dd92cbf48a835996e71cb9c7c016ebad.mp4?t=1771859962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage features a variety of weapons such as Japanese swords, kunai, and shuriken, as well as items that enhance weapons to advance the battle situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players who are skilled ninja can use special ninjutsu such as energy balls and aura shields.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311840/extras/1c4e36f639e4f49527daaebf1814d0a5.poster.avif?t=1771859962\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311840/extras/1c4e36f639e4f49527daaebf1814d0a5.webm?t=1771859962\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3311840/extras/1c4e36f639e4f49527daaebf1814d0a5.mp4?t=1771859962\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, enemies also attack with fire and lightning ninjutsu. In a ninja fight, one must carefully observe the enemy's actions and never miss the moment to strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Karakuri Ninja VR, as you progress through the stages, more powerful enemies will appear. Hone your swordsmanship and ninjutsu skills and face them bravely.</p>",
